            "title": "港股開升212點   科技及金融股俱升 AI概念續炒",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股恒生指數開報22027 點，升 212點或0.98%， 恒生科技指數開報5310，升75點或1.43%，恒生國企指數開報8063點，升870點或1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：快手網站\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230713-103127_source-web_01024_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：快手網站\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230713-103127_source-web_01024_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：快手網站</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">快手(01024)升3.32%，報51.35元 ; 第四範式(06682)升3.53%，報52.8元，成交入20大。京東(09618)升2.31%，報155元 ; 騰訊(00700)升1.77%，報449.8元 ; 美團(03690)升1.44%，報162元 ; 阿里巴巴(09988)升0.17%，報116.9元，成交居首。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">小米(01810)升1.8%，報42.4元。比亞迪(01211)升2.01%，報345.8元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">永利澳門(01128)升1.33%，報5.35元，第四季經調整物業EBITDA跌1.4%，全年升23.23%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">友邦(01299)升1.74%，報55.45元; 平保(02318)升1.23%，報45.45元。</p>\n</div>",
